OL,3,CMore than 5,500 outpatient
OL,4,Cappointments missed in Guernsey
OL,6,FMSG Chair Dr Steve Evans said: "It's
OL,7,Freally important that we make best use
OL,8,Fof our consultants' time so that they
OL,9,Fcan see as many patients as possible
OL,10,Fand reduce waiting times."
OL,12,FAround 6% of adult appointments were
OL,13,Feither not attended or cancelled with
OL,14,Fless than 24 hours' notice in 2023.
OL,16,FFor paediatric appointments,
OL,17,Fapproximately one in ten appointments
OL,18,Fwere missed.
