OL,6,FPhysiotherapy appointments have also
OL,7,Fseen high levels of non-attendance,
OL,8,Fwith 1,234 missed appointments
OL,9,F(approximately 9%) recorded last year.
OL,11,FHSC President Deputy Al Brouard said:
OL,12,F"Non-attendance is far more
OL,13,Fchallenging to manage than cancelling
OL,14,For re-arranging ahead of time.
OL,16,F"If adequate notice is given, the
OL,17,Fappointment can be reallocated to
OL,18,Fanother patient who needs our help.
